{"tid":300344,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係公海或者公海上空出世 個BB係咩國籍?","createTime":"2017-06-27T22:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T01:34:44.000Z","uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a23d305d092beeceea6b9ff283f0c86ccaa2c84c","tid":300344,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T22:13:37.000Z","msg":"請各位投票<br />\n<br />\nA. 韓國 因為人類係韓國起源<br />\nB. 巴拿馬 因為老豆老母同巴拿馬總統有交情<br />\nC. 中國 因為有中國血統都係中國人<br />\nD. 飛機註冊既國家<br />\nE. 無國籍"},{"pid":"8355fdaace7bf351aa56be869ba5393b4e073242","tid":300344,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T22:37:40.000Z","msg":"D/E, 睇下你㗎船邊度註冊"},{"pid":"2a5377ecc5bc8bf1987e0da3038aacde21349a3c","tid":300344,"uid":16783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T22:51:09.000Z","msg":"f 跟老豆老母"},{"pid":"621fb9649073e8caa6f240eb766f69783df85918","tid":300344,"uid":28704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T22:58:10.000Z","msg":"G 外星人"},{"pid":"34b3815bd7ee2bc8cb409161b705aec0c330877d","tid":300344,"uid":19322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:01:12.000Z","msg":"首先看父母的國籍，父母國籍所在國對新生兒國籍的規定。比如燈塔國承認雙重國籍，兲朝不承認雙重國籍的。<br />\n<br />\n這樣，嬰兒的國籍首先應該是跟隨父母的，國際慣例是跟父親，如果父母是不同國籍的話。<br />\n<br />\n其次看輪船的註冊國，看該國對新生兒的規定。在兲朝出生的外國嬰兒是不能天然享有兲朝國籍的。燈塔國最近對兲朝父母也有類似規定了。<br />\n<br />\n如果輪船註冊國允許登記國籍，那這孩子就多一個選擇。"},{"pid":"ed3a767dc39905807e5bc0a3ccbb9acabd4e618a","tid":300344,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:53:54.000Z","msg":"飛機好似係計目的地所屬國家？"},{"pid":"9cf3aad433354a6618e3e0280f0c95027280ad73","tid":300344,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:55:12.000Z","msg":"落地去醫院果個地方"},{"pid":"400f2aae1550670dcf4089ebd3f7ddbec5f5b0c2","tid":300344,"uid":125219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:34:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20151019/36848536/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Fheadline%2F20151019%2F36848536%2F&d=4CU04Cls7y1y4H5xr4VM4J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=5180aa34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20151019/36848536/</a>"}]}